  <Docs>
    <summary>Combines multiple draw operations with one material into a single draw operation.</summary>
    <remarks>When an instance of this class is placed in scope (by calling Begin), draw calls on supported objects (those implementing <see cref="T:GameStack.Graphics.IBatchable" />) will be batched into a single draw call per material. The actual draw takes place when the batch leaves scope.</remarks>
